function getPathCharType (ch) {
  if (ch === undefined || ch === null) { return 'eof' }

  const code = ch.charCodeAt(0);

  switch (code) {
    case 0x5B: // [
    case 0x5D: // ]
    case 0x2E: // .
    case 0x22: // "
    case 0x27: // '
      return ch

    case 0x5F: // _
    case 0x24: // $
    case 0x2D: // -
      return 'ident'

    case 0x09: // Tab
    case 0x0A: // Newline
    case 0x0D: // Return
    case 0xA0:  // No-break space
    case 0xFEFF:  // Byte Order Mark
    case 0x2028:  // Line Separator
    case 0x2029:  // Paragraph Separator
      return 'ws'
  }

  return 'ident'
}
